Author: TotallyNotARadar
Text: > I feel like getting help now is useless, because I haven’t relapsed yet.  Don’t wait until the house burns down to think about getting smoke detectors. The vast majority of health is about prevention. You get your flu shots (you do, don’t you??) because the little bit of discomfort is much better than the alternative. Your mental health is just the same. It’s not a good time but you need to take care of yourself

Author: Astronautee
Text: Really recommend reaching out to a professional tbh :/
